# Place Square APK files here
#
# Obtain with:
#   ./scripts/download_apk.sh
#   ./scripts/download_apk.sh --from /path/to/com.squareup.apk
#
# Expected files:
#   com.squareup.apk          — Square Point of Sale
#   com.squareup.team.apk     — Square Team (optional)
#   com.squareup.dashboard.apk — Square Dashboard (optional)
